OL,3,CAston Villa confirm #120m loss - but
OL,4,Cwhat does it mean for the future?
OL,6,Fhave published their finances for 2023
OL,7,Fand have confirmed a loss of just
OL,8,Funder #120 million, the highest in
OL,9,FEurope according to UEFA.
OL,11,FPremier League rules say that clubs
OL,12,Fcan lose a maximum of #105 million
OL,13,Fover a three-year period, meaning
OL,14,FVilla's finances are significantly
OL,15,Fover.
OL,17,FThe latest accounts show that wages
OL,18,Frose by nearly #60 million, and #63.7
OL,19,Fmillion was spent on new players.
