OL,6,FPlayer contracts also increased by #10
OL,7,Fmillion, despite #22 million made in
OL,8,Fplayer sales.
OL,10,FEven though the latest figures have
OL,11,Fleft many Villains worried, the club
OL,12,Fsay they feel confident that they're
OL,13,Foperating within the Premier League's
OL,14,Fspending rules.
OL,16,FThe club said: "It is important to
OL,17,Fnote that these figures are in line
OL,18,Fwith the strategic business plan, and
OL,19,Fwe continue to operate within the
OL,20,FPremier League's Profit and
OL,21,FSustainability rules.
