OL,4,Cwhat does it mean for the future?
OL,6,FEverton currently have a points
OL,7,Fdeduction for breaching Premier League
OL,8,Frules, and Nottingham Forest are
OL,9,Fwaiting to see if they share a similar
OL,10,Ffate.
